            <div class="visual-block block-2">ü§ù</div>
            <div class="visual-block block-3">üí´</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Values -->
    <section class="values">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
          <p>Our core values guide everything we do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">üéØ</div>
            <h3>Authenticity First</h3>
            <p>We believe the best content comes from genuine enthusiasm. We match creators with brands they actually love.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">‚öñÔ∏è</div>
            <h3>Fair Compensation</h3>
            <p>Creators deserve to be paid fairly for their work. We fight for competitive rates and transparent payments.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">üöÄ</div>
            <h3>Creator Growth</h3>
            <p>We're invested in your success. Our platform helps you build your portfolio and grow your career.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">üîí</div>
            <h3>Trust & Transparency</h3>
            <p>No hidden fees, no surprise terms. We believe in clear communication and honest relationships.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Story -->
    <section class="story">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="story-content">
          <span class="label">Our Story</span>
          <h2>Built by Creators, for Creators</h2>
          <p>We started this platform because we experienced the frustrations firsthand. As creators ourselves, we knew there had to be a better way to connect with brands without the endless email chains, unclear expectations, and delayed payments.</p>
          <p>What began as a simple idea has grown into a thriving community of creators and brands working together to produce amazing content. Every feature we build is designed with the creator experience in mind.</p>
