            <p>Building the future of creator marketing with passion and purpose.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-avatar">üë©‚Äçüíª</div>
            <h3>Head of Product</h3>
            <p>Crafting intuitive experiences that creators and brands love.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="team-member">
            <div class="member-avatar">üë®‚Äçüé®</div>
            <h3>Creator Relations</h3>
            <p>Supporting our community and ensuring creator success.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
          <p>Whether you're a creator looking to monetize your content or a brand seeking authentic voices, we'd love to have you.</p>
          <div class="cta-actions">
            <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-white">Join as Creator</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contact Us</a>
